[p 
	"Ghouls’n Ghosts in FBA is a little different from other ROM.It need some check.So you need have got another file besides recording file.It is FBA.roms.dat(
	[a class=extlink href=http://bbs.emufc.com/Xipo/FBA-roms.zip rel=nofollow 
		"in here
	]a
	"),please rename it and put it in \config\
	$LF
]p
